data.name: Label16.Text
data.value: LogicBox doesn't delete files fully when the delete button is pressed, instead it moves the deleted file or folder to the Recycle Bin on the server, this means that if you accidentally deleted a file, all you have to do is contact us and we'll restore it for you.

data.name: Label14.Text
data.value: Since LogicBox is internet based, you can take your files anywhere without worrying if they are on the next computer you use or not. If you have internet, you can easily get to the files you want and view or backup anything you like.

data.name: Label12.Text
data.value: We are LogicBox, a cloud storage service hosted by WindowsLogic Productions. We give you plans ranging from 25GB to 75GB. We like to think that an online backup service with plenty of storage doesn't have to cost loads and it's the reason we only charge you a minimum of £5.00/Month. We also host Minecraft servers for low prices too, these are manageable via the LogicBox interface.
